{"title":"windows下 python 'No module named pip'","date":"2019-01-02T02:41:56.000Z","slug":"NoModule","categories":["python"],"updated":"2019-01-02T02:46:24.333Z","content":"<p>原因是因为更换版本导致不能使用原来的pip</p>\n<p>cmd中敲命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">python -m ensurepip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>我做到上面这步就好了，但是网上给出的答案还有一步:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">easy_install pip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"Django模型层","slug":"ORM"},"next":{"title":"通过命令创建Django项目(虚拟环境中)","slug":"pythonvirtualenv"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/NoModule/"}